# WHAT THIS FIXES FROM THE PREVIOUS PLAN

## ❌ OLD PLAN PROBLEMS → ✅ NEW PLAN SOLUTIONS

**Too complex (7 rotating meals)**
→ 2 options per meal type, strict rotation

**Hidden calorie creep (fats everywhere)**  
→ ONE fat source per meal, measured strictly

**Too many snacks (5-6 eating events)**
→ 3-4 meals max, no grazing

**Unclear portions ("1 tbsp" = 1.5 tbsp in reality)**
→ Everything measured first 2 weeks, then you know portion sizes

**Fasted training sold as magic**
→ Just convenient timing, not a fat loss hack

**Slightly too high calories (2,300-2,400)**
→ 2,000-2,200 creates actual deficit

**Too many ingredients per meal**
→ 3-4 ingredients max per meal

